jmatrix

Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmatrix.Matrix
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IdentityMatrix, OneMatrix, ZeroMatrix

    public class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object
    The Matrix class represents numerical matrices, an m x n array of double values.
